{"tid":495579,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"摩連奴：球證犯下關鍵錯誤","createTime":"2017-12-10T19:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T19:44:38.000Z","uid":124292,"like":5,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c64542830e2331ce218042c5a82bcb3c0ab7551a","tid":495579,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:27:58.000Z","msg":"曼聯在主場1-2不敵曼城，球隊主教練摩連奴接受了賽後BBC的採訪。<br />\n<br />\n談到本場比賽判罰<br />\n<br />\n我的第一反應是我為球證感到遺憾，因為他吹了一場很好的比賽，但不幸的是他還是犯下了一個關鍵的失誤。<br />\n<br />\n比賽結果被靴里拉那次沒有被吹罰的十二碼所影響了，那個球本來讓我們可以把比分扳成2-2的平局，這樣的話之後我們還有20分鐘的比賽可以爭取。球證很不走運，因為那顯然很清楚是一個十二碼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/football/40955919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Flive%2Ffootball%2F40955919&d=lq%2FtfruxcB6Dm%2BW33ACWXx4KspRE1ZdqvS7v6cf6aI4%3D&h=50dfbd90\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Flive%2Ffootball%2F40955919&h=b0797305\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bbc.com/sport/live/football/40955919</a>"},{"pid":"35eef5e450c2f52020293ec36ed7e34fa1ce74a1","tid":495579,"uid":124292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:44:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}